  hom‚ÇÅ : T‚ÇÅ.obj‚ÇÅ ‚ü∂ T‚ÇÇ.obj‚ÇÅ
  /-- the second morphism in a triangle morphism -/
  hom‚ÇÇ : T‚ÇÅ.obj‚ÇÇ ‚ü∂ T‚ÇÇ.obj‚ÇÇ
  /-- the third morphism in a triangle morphism -/
  hom‚ÇÉ : T‚ÇÅ.obj‚ÇÉ ‚ü∂ T‚ÇÇ.obj‚ÇÉ
